{"tid":1374650,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"北韓指西方國家指使香港反修例示威","createTime":"2019-07-27T22:13:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-28T03:32:32.000Z","uid":278587,"like":58,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":35,"replies":[{"pid":"2d13d159eea1e6bb25df4d1b0eab41b5473e1282","tid":1374650,"uid":278587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T22:13:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bCuWKg5etbc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbCuWKg5etbc&d=ajJRCbjZ3CJF8zdY8%2Fu%2F1wAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=a7145847\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bCuWKg5etbc</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://images-news.now.com/newsimage/NewsImage/NK-HK-190727-17.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages-news.now.com%2Fnewsimage%2FNewsImage%2FNK-HK-190727-17.jpg&h=0ab7ea60&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【Now新聞台】北韓罕有評論香港的反逃犯條例修訂示威，指是有西方國家指使，破壞社會及政治穩定。<br />\n<br />\n《勞動新聞》周五發表的署名評論文章指出，香港近期有一股不純勢力受西方國家指使，以反修訂逃犯條例為藉口，肆意損壞公共設施，衝擊警察總部及立法會大樓，破壞社會穩定。<br />\n<br />\n文章又指，事實清楚表明香港事態是美國等西方國家及香港分裂勢力狼狽為奸，企圖阻撓中國發展及分裂中國的陰謀產物。<br />\n<br />\n評論指，任何國家、組織及個人都無權干涉香港事務，又指香港事務純屬中國內政，必須按照中國人民意願解決。北韓支持中國黨及政府，為解決香港事態所採取的措施。"},{"pid":"31a122752faf736e3b3d37d82676218e5a3f356c","tid":1374650,"uid":189328,"like":65,"dislike":0,"score":65,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T22:24:54.000Z","msg":"搵個極權國家批評人， 算唔算助攻<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa0e3f0d2b88427b9014bc16e110749d824fca83","tid":1374650,"uid":101537,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T22:25:56.000Z","msg":"北韓嘅Statement who fucking cares?"},{"pid":"9d76f19bcc288090e2e66e539000e0669b439c7b","tid":1374650,"uid":51701,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"fa0e3f0d2b88427b9014bc16e110749d824fca83","tid":1374650,"uid":101537,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T22:25:56.000Z","msg":"北韓嘅Statement who fucking cares?"